登录后发表评论','View Comments'=>'查看评论','Last edited %1$s by %2$s'=>'最近由 %2$s 编辑的 %1$s','Reply to'=>'回复','Manage Comment'=>'管理评论','Spoiler Title'=>'剧透标题','You cannot rate again'=>'你不能再评分了','You\'re not allowed to rate here'=>'你不能在这里评分','Are you sure you want to delete this attachment?'=>'您确定要删除此附件吗？','Not allowed file type'=>'不允许的文件类型','Maximum number of uploaded files is'=>'上载档案的最大数量为上载档案的最大数量为','Maximum upload file size is'=>'最大上传文件大小为','Maximum post size is'=>'最大帖子大小为','Uploading in progress! Please wait.'=>'正在上传中！请稍候。','Attach an image to this comment'=>'将图像附加到此评论','Change the attached image'=>'更改附件图像','File is empty. Please upload something more substantial. This error could also be caused by uploads being disabled in your php.ini or by post_max_size being defined as smaller than upload_max_filesize in php.ini.'=>'文件为空。请上传一些更充实的东西。此错误也可能是由于 php 中的上载被禁用, 或者由 post_max_size 定义为小于 upload_max_filesize 的 php. ini。','Post ID not exists'=>'帖子ID不存在','Sorry, uploading not allowed for this post'=>'抱歉，此帖子不允许上传','You do not have sufficient permissions to perform this action'=>'您没有足够的权限执行此操作','Hacker?'=>'黑客 ?','Stop doing this!!!'=>'停止这样做!!!','Settings updated'=>'设置已更新','Phrases updated'=>'短语已更新','Options Imported Successfully!'=>'选项导入成功！','Error occured! File content is empty or data is not valid!'=>'发生了错误！ 文件内容为空或数据无效！','Error occured! Can not get file content!'=>'发生了错误！ 无法获取文件内容！','Error occured! Please choose file!'=>'发生了错误！ 请选择文件！','Phrases Imported Successfully!'=>'短语成功导入！','Please complete required steps to start using wpDiscuz 7'=>'请完成所需的步骤以开始使用wpDiscuz 7','Go to Update Wizard &raquo;'=>'转到更新向导＆raquo;','Go to Installation Wizard &raquo;'=>'转到安装向导＆raquo;','Jetpack Comments are active.'=>'Jetpack注释处于活动状态。','Comment votes meta data need to be regenerated'=>'评论票数元数据需要重新生成','Regenerate Vote Metas'=>'重新生成投票元','Closed Comments data need be regenerated'=>'封闭评论数据需要重新生成','Regenerate Closed Comments'=>'重新生成已关闭的评论','Comments votes data need to be regenerated'=>'评论票数数据需要重新生成','Regenerate Vote Data'=>'重新生成投票数据','Please synchronize comment data for the best performance and fastest experience'=>'请同步评论数据以获得最佳性能和最快体验','Synchronize Commenters Data'=>'同步评论者数据','Please rebuild ratings for the best performance and fastest experience'=>'请重建评级以获得最佳性能和最快体验','Rebuild Ratings'=>'重建评级','Comment Form Settings'=>'评论表单设置','Keep guest commenter credentials in browser cookies for X days'=>'在浏览器Cookie中将访客评论者凭据保留X天','wpDiscuz uses WordPress functions to keep guest Name, Email and Website information in cookies. Those are used to fill according fields of comment form on next commenting time. Set this option value -1 to make it unlimited. Set this option value 0 to clear those data when user closes browser.'=>'wpDiscuz使用WordPress功能将访客名称，电子邮件和网站信息保留在cookie中。这些用于在下一次评论时根据评论表填写字段。将此选项值设置为-1使其不受限制。将此选项值设置为0可在用户关闭浏览器时清除这些数据。','Comment author name length (for guests only)'=>'评论作者姓名的长度（仅限游客）','Comment Form View'=>'评论','By default, only the comment text field is visible. When you click on the comment text field it opens all other fields (Name, Email, Website, etc...). If you want to keep all fields open, please set this option "expended".'=>'默认情况下，仅注释文本字段可见。当您单击注释文本字段时，它将打开所有其他字段（名称，电子邮件，网站等...）。如果您希望所有字段保持打开状态，请将此选项设置为“ expended”。','Enable drop animation for comment form and subscription bar'=>'为评论表单和订阅栏启用放动画','Load Rich Editor'=>'加载富编辑器','Search engines rank web pages for mobile devices totally different. For the mobile devices, there are more restrictions for JS and CSS files loading. This is the main reason why wpDiscuz disables the Rich Editor for mobile devices by default. It\'s only enabled for desktop. If you have good cache and website optimizer plugins you can enable the rich editor for mobile devices as well.'=>'搜索引擎对移动设备的网页进行完全不同的排名。对于移动设备，对加载 JS 和 CSS 文件有更多的限制。这是 wpDiscuz 默认情况下禁用移动设备的富编辑器的主要原因。它仅启用桌面。如果你有良好的缓存和网站优化插件，你可以启用丰富的编辑器的移动设备。','Rich Editor Toolbar Buttons'=>'丰富的编辑器工具栏按钮','Please click on buttons to disable or enable. The enabled buttons are colored green, the disabled buttons are gray. If you want to disable the whole formatting toolbar, please click on the [Disable formatting buttons] button. Options to manage Image Attachment button are located in \'Comment Content and Media\' setting page.'=>'请单击按钮以禁用或启用。启用的按钮为绿色，禁用的按钮为灰色。如果要禁用整个格式设置工具栏，请单击 [禁用格式设置按钮] 按钮。管理图像附件按钮的选项位于"评论内容和媒体"设置页中。','Enable Quicktags'=>'启用快速标签','Quicktag is a on-click button that inserts HTML in to comment textarea. For example the "b" Quicktag will insert the HTML bold tags < b > < /b >.'=>'QuestTAG是一个单击HTML按钮，将HTML插入到评论文本中。例如，“B”QueGTAG将插入HTML粗体标签<b> < /b>。','Site Key'=>'网站密钥','Secret Key'=>'密钥','reCAPTCHA Theme'=>'reCAPTCHA主题','reCAPTCHA Language'=>'reCAPTCHA语言','Request Method'=>'请求方法','Enable for Guests'=>'为游客启用','Enable for Logged-in Users'=>'为登录用户启用','Display on Subscription Form'=>'在订阅表格上显示','User Authorization and Profile Data'=>'用户授权和配置文件数据','Display logged-in user name and logout link on comment form'=>'在评论表单上显示登录的用户名和注销链接','Show "Login" link on comment form'=>'在评论表单上显示“登录”链接','"My Content and Settings" button'=>'“我的内容和设置”按钮','The "My Content & Settings" button is located in comment filter panel on top of all comments, right after the [X Comments] phrase. This button opens a pop-up window allowing commenters manage their content and settings.'=>'“我的内容和设置”按钮位于所有评论顶部的评论过滤器面板中，紧接在[X评论]短语之后。 此按钮将打开一个弹出窗口，允许评论者管理其内容和设置。','Enable Profiles URL'=>'启用个人资料网址','By default wpDiscuz adds a link with comment author avatar to the author profile page, you can disable this link using this option. However in case you use some plugin with User Profile page, you should keep this option enabled. wpDiscuz is well integrated with %s, BuddyPress and Ultimate Member profile builder plugins.'=>'默认情况下，wpDiscuz将带有注释作者头像的链接添加到作者个人资料页面，您可以使用此选项禁用此链接。但是，如果您在“用户配置文件”页面上使用某些插件，则应保持启用此选项。 wpDiscuz与 %s，BuddyPress和Ultimate Member个人资料生成器插件很好地集成在一起。','Use Website URL as Profile URL'=>'显示网站URL字段','Use guest email to detect registered account'=>'使用游客邮箱匹配已注册账户','Sometimes registered users comment as guest using the same email address. wpDiscuz can detect the account role using guest email and display commenter label correctly.'=>'有时注册用户未登录时使用相同的邮箱来评论。wpDiscuz可以基于游客邮箱探测账户并正确显示评论人','Login URL'=>'登录网址','[REDIRECT_URL]'=>'重定向至URL：','Social Login and Share'=>'社交登录和共享','User agreement prior to a social login action'=>'社交登录操作之前的用户协议','If this option is enabled, all Social Login buttons become not-clickable until user accept automatic account creation process based on his/her Social Network Account shared information (email, name). This checkbox and appropriate information will be displayed when user click on a social login button, prior to the login process. This extra step is added to comply with the GDPR'=>'如果启用此选项，则在用户接受基于其社交网络帐户共享信息（电子邮件，姓名）的自动帐户创建过程之前，所有社交登录按钮都将变为不可点击。 当用户在登录过程之前单击社交登录按钮时，将显示此复选框和相应信息。 添加此额外步骤以符合GDPR','The note text and the label of this checkbox can be managed in Comments > Phrases > Social Login tab.'=>'注释文本和此复选框的标签可以在“评论”>“短语”>“社交登录”选项卡中进行管理。','Display social login buttons on reply forms'=>'在回复表单上显示社交登录按钮','Display Social Networks Avatars'=>'显示社交网络头像','Display Social Network Icon on User Avatars'=>'在用户阿凡达上显示社交网络图标','Remember Logged-in Status'=>'记住登录状态','Facebook Login Button'=>'Facebook 登录按钮','Use Facebook OAuth2'=>'使用 Facebook OAuth2','If you enable this option, please make sure you\'ve inserted the Valid OAuth Redirect URI in according field when you create Facebook Login App. Your website OAuth Redirect URI is displayed above.'=>'如果啟用此選項，請確保在創建 Facebook Login App 時在相應欄位中插入了有效 OAuth 重新導向 URI。你的網站 OAuth 重新導向 URI 顯示在上方。','Facebook Share Button'=>'Facebook分享按钮图标','Facebook Application ID'=>'Facebook应用程序ID','Facebook Application Secret'=>'Facebook应用密钥','Google Login Button'=>'谷歌登录按钮','Google Client ID'=>'Google客户端ID','Google Client Secret'=>'Google客户端秘密','Disqus Login Button'=>'Disqus登录按钮','Disqus Public Key'=>'取消公钥','Disqus Secret Key'=>'否认密钥','WordPress Login Button'=>'WordPress登录按钮','WordPress Client ID'=>'Wordpress 客户端 ID','WordPress Client Secret'=>'WordPress 客户端密钥','Instagram Login Button'=>'Instagram登录按钮','Instagram App ID'=>'Instagram 应用ID','Instagram App Secret'=>'Instagram 应用密钥','LinkedIn Login Button'=>'隐藏投票按钮','LinkedIn Client ID'=>'Instagram 客户 ID','LinkedIn Client Secret'=>'linkedin 客户端秘钥','WhatsApp Share Button'=>'WhatsApp分享按钮图标','Yandex Login Button'=>'隐藏投票按钮','Yandex ID'=>'Yandex ID','Yandex Password'=>'Yandex 密码','Weibo Login Button'=>'微博登录按钮','Weibo App Key'=>'微博 - App Key','Weibo App Secret'=>'微博应用秘密','WeChat Login Button'=>'微信登录按钮','WeChat App ID'=>'微信应用 ID','WeChat Secret'=>'微信密钥','QQ Login Button'=>'登录按钮','QQ AppID'=>'QQ AppID','QQ AppKey'=>'QQ AppKey','Baidu Login Button'=>'隐藏投票按钮','Baidu Client ID'=>'百度客户端 ID','Baidu Client Secret'=>'百度客户端机密','App ID'=>'App ID','Article and Comment Rating'=>'文章和评论评分','Enable Aggregate Rating Schema'=>'启用聚合评级架构','Aggregate rating schema is a code integrated with post rating HTML. This enables Google to feature your post ratings and attract customers with it. When searching the internet, people will see your posts search results with star ratings. Even though those results are not at the top of search engine results page, those sites caught people attention first.'=>'聚合评级架构是一个与后评级 HTML 集成的代码。这使 Google 能够提供您的帖子评级，并吸引客户使用该帖子。搜索互联网时，人们会看到你的帖子搜索结果与星级。尽管这些结果不在搜索引擎结果页面的顶部，但这些网站首先引起了人们的注意。','Aggregate rating schema is a code integrated with post rating HTML. This enables Google to feature your post ratings and attract customers with it. When searching the internet, people will see your posts search results with star ratings. Even though those results are not at the top of search engine results page, those sites caught people attention first. If your website does not sell Products, we do not recommend activating this option. For more details, please %s.'=>'聚合评级模式是与后评级 HTML 集成的代码。这使得 Google 能够提供您的帖子评级并吸引客户。搜索互联网时，人们会看到你的帖子搜索结果与星级。尽管这些结果不在搜索引擎结果页面的顶部，但这些网站首先还是引起了人们的注意。如果您的网站不销售产品，我们不建议激活此选项。欲了解更多详情，请%s。','Display Ratings'=>'显示评分','Rating Star Colors'=>'评级星色','Comment Thread Displaying'=>'注释线程显示','Comment List Loading Type'=>'注释列表加载类型','Keep your page loading speed high by disabling comments loading. Once the page loading is complete, this option will initiate AJAX request and load comments without affecting page loading speed. Also, you can select the [View Comments] button option to allow visitors load comments manually whenever they want.'=>'通过禁用评论加载来保持页面加载速度较高。页面加载完成后，此选项将启动AJAX请求并加载注释，而不会影响页面加载速度。另外，您可以选择[查看评论]按钮选项，以允许访问者在需要时手动加载评论。','Display only parent comments and <u>view replies &or;</u> button'=>'仅显示主评论和<u>查看回复＆或; </ u>按钮','If this option is enabled only parent comments will be displayed. This increases page load speed and keeps pages light. If visitor wants to read replies he/she just need to click on [view replies (12)] button located on all parent comments which have replies.'=>'如果启用此选项，则仅显示父注释。这会增加页面加载速度并保持页面轻盈。如果访问者想要阅读回复，他/她只需要点击[查看回复（12）]按钮，该按钮位于所有有回复的父评论上。','Display "Most Reacted Comments" filter button'=>'显示“反应最多的评论”过滤器按钮','Display "Hottest Comment Threads" filter button'=>'显示“最热门的评论主题”过滤器按钮','Display Comment Sorting Options'=>'显示注释排序选项','This option enables comment sorting buttons (newest | oldest | most voted). Sorting buttons are not available for the default comments pagination type [1][2][3]... It\'s only active for [Load more] and other AJAX pagination types.'=>'此选项启用评论排序按钮（最新|最旧|最多投票）。 排序按钮不适用于默认评论分页类型[1] [2] [3] ...它仅对[加载更多]和其他AYAX分页类型有效。','Set comments order to "Most voted" by default'=>'默认情况下将注释顺序设置为"投票最多"','Reverse Child Comments Order'=>'反向子评论排序','By default child comments are sorted by oldest on top. Using this option you can revers child comments order and sort them by newest on top.'=>'默认情况下，子注释按顶部的最早排序。使用此选项，您可以对子注释顺序进行重新排列，并按顶部的最新排序。','Comments Pagination Type'=>'注释分页类型','You can manage the number of comments for [Load more] option in Settings > Discussion page, using "Break comments into pages with [X] top level comments per page" option. To show the default Wordpress comment pagination you should enable the checkbox on beginning of the same option.'=>'您可以在設置 -> 討論 頁面,為[加載更多]管理評論數量,使用"每頁一級評論數量達到 [X] 時分頁" 的選項.若要顯示wordpress默認的評論分頁,您需要啟用相同的選項.','Highlight Unread Comments'=>'突出显示未读评论','Scroll to the comment after posting'=>'发布后滚动到注释','Newest and oldest comment ordering by'=>'最新和最古老的评论订购','Comment Thread Features'=>'注释线程功能','Show Comment Link'=>'显示评论文字：','Show Comment Date'=>'显示注释日期','Show Voting Buttons'=>'显示投票按钮','Voting Buttons Icon'=>'投票按钮图标','Comment Voting Result Mode'=>'评论投票结果模式','Enable down vote button (dislike)'=>'启用向下投票按钮（不喜欢）','Allow Guests to Vote for Comments'=>'允许客人投票征求意见','Highlight Voting Buttons for Voters'=>'突出显示选民的投票按钮','This allows users to see own voted comments.'=>'这使用户可以查看自己的投票评论。','Display Avatars'=>'显示头像','This option only related to avatars in comment system. For sitewide avatar control, please use WordPress native avatar settings in Dashboard > Settings > Discussions admin page.'=>'此选项仅与注释系统中的头像相关。对于全站点的头像控件，请使用仪表板设置中的 WordPress 本机>设置>讨论管理页面。','Default Avatar Source URL for Users'=>'用户的默认头像源URL','Default Avatar Source URL for Guests'=>'来宾的默认阿凡达源 URL','Enable Sitewide Usage of Default Avatars'=>'启用默认阿凡达的站点使用','Styles and Colors'=>'样式和颜色','Comment Form and Comment List Style'=>'评论表单和评论列表样式','Starting from wpDiscuz 7 you can choose the [ Off ] option of comment style. It\'ll remove most of wpDiscuz CSS code and allow you write your own CSS for custom comment styling.'=>'从 wpDiscuz 7 开始，您可以选择评论风格的 [关闭] 选项。它将删除大部分wpDiscuz CSS代码，并允许您编写自己的CSS进行自定义评论造型。','Style Specific Colors'=>'样式特定颜色','These options allows you manage comment section colors individaly for the Default and Dark Styles'=>'这些选项使您可以分别管理默认样式和深色样式的注释部分颜色','General Colors'=>'常规颜色','Comment Text Size'=>'注释文本大小','Load Font Awesome css lib'=>'加载字体真棒 css lib','IMPORTANT: In case your theme uses old versions of Font-Awesome lib, you should not disable this this option. The theme old version doesn\'t support new version icons, thus some wpDiscuz icons might be lost.'=>'重要说明：如果您的主题使用旧版本的Font-Awesome lib，则不应禁用此选项。主题旧版本不支持新版本的图标，因此某些wpDiscuz图标可能会丢失。','Custom CSS Code'=>'自定义CSS代码','Subscription and User Following'=>'订阅和用户关注','Enable User Mentioning'=>'启用用户提及','This option allows mentioning users in comments using @nicename method. Mentioned users will get notification via email if the next option is enabled. To get an advanced user mentioning features and to be able mention comments by #CommentID, we recommend the %s addon.'=>'此选项允许使用@nicename方法在注释中提及用户。如果启用了下一个选项，则上述用户将通过电子邮件收到通知。要获得高级用户提及功能并能够通过#CommentID提及评论，我们建议使用%s插件。','Send E-Mail Notification to Mentioned Users'=>'向提及的用户发送电子邮件通知','Notify comment author once comment is approved'=>'评论一经批准，即通知评论作者','Enable subscription confirmation for registered users'=>'为注册用户启用订阅确认','Enable subscription confirmation for guests'=>'启用访客订阅确认功能','Subscription types in Subscription Bar drop-down'=>'订阅栏下拉列表中的订阅类型','Display "Notify of new replies to this comment" option in comment form'=>'以评论形式显示"通知此评论的新回复"选项','wpDiscuz is the only comment plugin which allows you to subscribe to certain comment replies. This option is located above [Post Comment] button in comment form. You can disable this subscription way by unchecking this option.'=>'wpDiscuz是唯一允许您针对特定的评论订阅的评论插件。此选项在 [发表评论] 按钮前显示，您可以取消勾选、禁用此功能。','Keep checked the "Notify of new replies to this comment" option by default'=>'默认情况下，请选中"通知此注释的新答复"选项','Enable User Following Feature'=>'启用用户关注功能','Follow users without email confirmation'=>'关注用户，无需确认电子邮','Email subject'=>'电子邮件主题','Email content'=>'邮件内容','User Labels and Badges'=>'用户标签和徽章','Display Comment Author Labels'=>'显示评论作者标签','Comment Author Label Colors by User Role'=>'注释作者标签颜色（按用户角色）','Comment Moderation'=>'评论审核','Edit Button - Allow comment editing for'=>'编辑按钮 - 允许评论编辑给','Enable editing for replied comments'=>'启用编辑已回复的评论','Display comment editing Information'=>'显示注释编辑信息','Stick Button - Stick a comment thread'=>'置顶按钮-置顶评论','Close Button - Close a comment thread'=>'关闭按钮-关闭一条评论对话','Limit Comments per User'=>'限制每个用户的注释','This option allows control commenting activity per user. You can set maximum number of comments users can leave per post or sitewide. It also allow to set restriction for comments or for replies only.'=>'此选项允许控制每个用户的注释活动。您可以设置用户每次帖子或在全站点范围内可以留下的最大评论数量。它还允许只对评论或答复设置限制。','Comment Content and Media'=>'评论内容和媒体','Comment Text Length'=>'注释文本长度','Allows to set minimum and maximum number of chars can be inserted in comment textarea. Leave the max value empty to remove the limit.'=>'允许设置可在注释文本域中插入的最小和最大字符数。 将最大值保留为空以删除限制。','Reply Text Length'=>'评论文本长度','Allows to set minimum and maximum number of chars can be inserted in reply textarea. Leave the max value empty to remove the limit.'=>'允许设置最小和最大字符数可以插入回复文本区域。将最大值留空以删除限制。','Image Source URL to Image Conversion'=>'图片来源网址到图片的转换','Enable WordPress Shortcodes in Comment Content'=>'在评论内容中启用 WordPress 短代码','This option allows embedding other plugins shortcodes in comment content. Some plugin shortcodes work very slow, so this may affect your page load speed if the shortcode provider plugin is not well optimized.'=>'此选项允许在注释内容中嵌入其他插件的短代码。某些插件短码工作非常缓慢，因此，如果短代码提供程序插件没有很好地优化，这可能会影响您的页面加载速度。','The number of words before breaking comment text (Read more)'=>'断开注释文本之前的单词数（了解更多）','Set this option value 0, to turn off comment text breaking function.'=>'设置为0，则关闭评论文本缩略功能。','Enable Media Uploading'=>'启用媒体上传','This option allows commenters to attach an image with comments.'=>'此选项使评论者可以在图像上附加评论。','Allow Media Uploading for Guests'=>'允许为来宾上传媒体','Enable Lightbox for Attached Images'=>'为附加图像启用灯箱','Allowed File Types'=>'允许的文件类型','Max Uploaded Size'=>'最大上传大小','You can not set this value more than \'upload_max_filesize\' and \'post_max_size\'. If you want to increase server parameters please contact to your hosting service support.'=>'不能将此值设置为"upload_max_filesize"和"post_max_size"。如果您想增加服务器参数，请联系您的托管服务支持。','Show Comments Media in Dashboard'=>'在仪表板中显示评论媒体','Single Image Sizes in Comments'=>'注释中的单个图像大小','Generate Thumbnail Sizes'=>'生成缩略图大小','Once image is uploaded, it\'ll generate thumbnails according to your selected sizes. When you set up a new WordPress website, the platform gives you three image sizes to play with: thumbnail, medium, and large (plus the file\'s original resolution). You may have other options and sizes which are registered by current active theme and by other plugins.'=>'图片上传后，会根据您选择的尺寸生成缩略图。当您建立新的WordPress网站时，该平台会为您提供三种图像尺寸供您使用：缩略图，中号和大号（加上文件的原始分辨率）。您可能还有其他选项和大小，这些选项和大小由当前活动主题和其他插件注册。','Live Commenting and Notifications'=>'实时评论和通知','Comment Bubble'=>'评论气泡','Comment Bubble is a real-time updating sticky comment icon on your web pages. It invites people to comment, displays current comments information and notifies current page viewers about new comments.'=>'评论气泡是实时更新网页上的粘性注释图标。它邀请用户评论、显示当前评论信息，并通知当前页面查看者有关新评论。','Comment Bubble Live Update'=>'评论泡泡实时更新','Comment Bubble Location'=>'评论气泡位置','Bubble - Notify on New Comments'=>'气泡 - 通知新评论','If the Bubble live update is enabled, it shows new comments excerpts as a pop-up information to article reads in real-time. This keeps website visitors up to date and engages them join to the discussion.'=>'如果启用了气泡实时更新，它将显示新评论摘录，作为实时阅读文章的弹出信息。这可以使网站访问者保持最新状态，并吸引他们加入讨论。','Bubble - Invite to comment in X seconds'=>'气泡 - 邀请在 X 秒内发表评论','In most cases article readers don\'t even think about leaving some comment. Using this option you can enable Bubble &laquo;Invite to Comment&raquo; message. Once page is loaded and visitor has read some content, it reminds about comments and calls to leave a reply.'=>'在大多数情况下，文章读者甚至都不会考虑发表评论。使用此选项，您可以启用气泡“邀请发表评论”消息。加载页面并访问者阅读了某些内容后，它会提醒您有关评论和呼叫的信息，以供回复。','Bubble - Hide the invitation message in X seconds'=>'气泡 - 在 X 秒内隐藏邀请消息','Live Update'=>'在线更新','wpDiscuz live update is very light and doesn\'t overload your server. However we recommend to monitor your server resources if you\'re on a Shared hosting plan. There are some very weak hosting plans which may not be able to perform very frequently live update requests. If you found some issue you can set the option below 1 minute or more.'=>'wpDiscuz实时更新非常轻，不会使服务器过载。 但是，如果您使用共享主机方案，我们建议您监控服务器资源。 有一些非常弱的托管计划可能无法执行非常频繁的实时更新请求。 如果您发现某些问题，可以将选项设置为低于30秒或更长时间。','Enable Live Update for Guests'=>'为来宾启用实时更新','Update Comment List Every'=>'更新評論列表,每','Inline Commenting'=>'内联评论','Display filter button to load inline feedbacks'=>'显示过滤器按钮以加载内联反馈','This filter button appears next to all filter buttons and comment sorting options. It allows to filter and display article inline feedbacks (comments made while reading current article).'=>'该过滤器按钮出现在所有过滤器按钮和注释排序选项旁边。 它允许过滤和显示文章内联反馈（阅读当前文章时发表的评论）。','Animation for "Leave a Feedback" button in article content'=>'文章内容中"留下反馈"按钮的动画','Once a question is added in article editor (backend), readers will see a small comment icon (call to leave a feedback) next to the text part you\'ve selected for your question on article (front-end). This icon calls people to leave a feedback, using the type you\'ve selected in this option. For example, if you\'ve chosen the "Blink" option, once reader scrolled  and reached to the article text with question, it animates with comment button size and color changes attracting readers attention.'=>'在文章编辑器（后端）中添加问题后，读者将看到您为文章（前端）问题选择的文本部分旁边有一个小注释图标（调用以留下反馈）。此图标调用用户使用您选择的类型留下反馈。例如，如果您选择了"闪烁"选项，一旦读者滚动并到达有问题的文章文本，它将使用注释按钮大小和颜色更改来设置动画，从而吸引读者的注意。','General Settings'=>'通用设置','Enable wpDiscuz on Home Page'=>'在主页上启用wpDiscuz','Use WordPress native AJAX functions'=>'使用WordPress自带的AJAX功能','By disabling this option you\'re automatically enabling wpDiscuz custom AJAX functions, which are many times faster that the default WordPress functions. Just make sure it doesn\'t conflict with your plugins.'=>'通过禁用此选项，您将自动启用wpDiscuz自定义AJAX函数，这些函数比默认WordPress函数快许多倍。 只要确保它不会与您的插件冲突。','Combine JS and CSS Files to Optimize Page Loading Speed'=>'组合 JS 和 CSS 文件以优化页面加载速度','Minify JS and CSS Files to Optimize Page Loading Speed'=>'组合 JS 和 CSS 文件以优化页面加载速度','Secure comment content in HTTPS protocol.'=>'使用HTTPS协议保护评论内容。','This option detects images and other contents with non-https source URLs and fix according to your selected logic.'=>'此选项使用非https源URL检测图像和其他内容，并根据您选择的逻辑进行修复。','Redirect First Comment to'=>'将第一个注释重定向到','Use WordPress Date/Time Format'=>'使用WordPress日期/時間格式','wpDiscuz shows Human Readable date format. If you check this option it\'ll show the date/time format set in WordPress General Settings.'=>'wpDiscuz显示人机友好的日期格式。如果你勾选此项，将按WordPress通用设置来显示。','Structure of Human Readable Date Format'=>'人类可读日期格式的结构','By default, comment date is displayed with the human readable format, such as [X days ago]. For some languages, you may need to change the sequence of words in this date. This option provides shordcodes for each word allowing you manage the order. [number] is the \'X\', [time_unit] is the \'days\', [adjective] is the \'ago\'.'=>'默认情况下，注释日期以人类可读格式显示，例如 [X 天前]。对于某些语言，您可能需要更改此日期中的单词顺序。此选项为每个单词提供密码，允许您管理订单。[数字] 是 "X"， [time_unit] 是 "天"， [形容词] 是 "前" 。','Use Plugin .PO/.MO Files'=>'使用外掛的 .PO/.MO 文件','wpDiscuz phrase system allows you to translate all front-end phrases. However if you have a multi-language website it\'ll not allow you to add more than one language translation. The only way to get it is the plugin translation files (.PO / .MO). If wpDiscuz has the languages you need you should check this option to disable phrase system and it\'ll automatically translate all phrases based on language files according to current language.'=>'wpDiscuz短语设置允许你翻译所有前端字段。但是，如果你有多语言站点那么你需要使用 (.PO / .MO)翻译文件。wpDiscuz将根据当前语言显示前端字段。','Help wpDiscuz to grow allowing people to recognize which comment plugin you use'=>'显示wpDiscuz插件标识，帮助wpDiscuz成长','Please check this option on to help wpDiscuz get more popularity as your thank to the hard work we do for you totally free. This option adds a very small (16x16px) icon under the comment section which will allow your site visitors recognize the name of comment solution you use.'=>'勾选此项，以帮助wpDiscuz更受欢迎，因为您感谢我们为您完全免费的努力工作。此选项在评论部分添加了一个非常小的（16x16px）图标，这将允许您的网站访问者识别您使用的评论插件名称。','Enable Cache'=>'启用缓存','Enable Comments and Users Cache'=>'启用注释和用户缓存','Cache Reset Frequency'=>'缓存重置频率','Remove Vote Data'=>'移除投票數據','Purge Comment and User Caches'=>'隐藏评论人标签','wpDiscuz Addons'=>'wpDiscuz附加组件','wpDiscuz Add-ons'=>'wpDiscuz附加组件','Addons Support Forum'=>'插件支持论坛','All wpDiscuz addons are being developed by wpDiscuz developers at gVectors Team. These addons help us to keep top level development of the free wpDiscuz plugin. All essential and even dozens of extra-cool features are already available for free in the core wpDiscuz plugin. There are not any limits, any pro and paid versions of wpDiscuz. We have another dozens of awesome features in our to-do list which will be added for free in the future releases.'=>'所有 wpDiscuz 插件都由 wpDiscuz 开发人员在 gVectors 团队开发。这些附加组件帮助我们保持免费wpDiscuz插件的顶层开发。所有必要的，甚至几十个超酷的功能已经是免费的核心wpDiscuz插件。没有任何限制， 任何专业和付费版本的 wpDiscuz 。我们还有几十个真棒功能在我们的即用列表中，这将在未来的版本中免费添加。',' Thank you!<br/> Sincerely yours,<br/> gVectors Team&nbsp;'=>'谢谢您!<br/>此致，<br/> gvectors团队&nbsp；','Installed'=>'已安装','at least'=>'至少','More Info &raquo;'=>'阅读更多 &raquo;','Live Preview | Buy'=>'实时预览| 购买','More information about'=>'更多信息','View wpDiscuz Addons Bundle'=>'查看wpDiscuz插件包','wpDiscuz Addons Bundle'=>'wpDiscuz Addons Bundle','Welcome to wpDiscuz 7'=>'欢迎来到 wpDiscuz 7','Built to Engage'=>'专为参与而打造','Thank you for installing wpDiscuz!'=>'感谢您安装wpDiscuz !','wpDiscuz 7 is a revolution in WordPress commenting experience.'=>'wordpress评论wpDiscuz 7是一个革命的经验。','This version is mostly focused on website visitors engagement,'=>'这个版本主要关注网站访问者参与,','It\'s totally improved with brand new innovative features bringing live to your website and discussions.'=>'完全改善了全新的创新特性将活到你的网站和讨论。','What\'s New'=>'新功能','Inline Feedback'=>'内联的反馈','Live Notification, Bubble!'=>'实时通知，气泡！','Comment Layouts'=>'评论布局','Social Login and Commenting'=>'社会登录和评论','Article Rating vs Rating Field'=>'文章评级和评级','Article Inline Feedback'=>'内嵌条反馈','First time in blog commenting experience we introduce, the Inline Feedback feature. This is an interactive article reading option with questions and feedback. Now article authors can add some questions for readers on certain part of article content and ask for feedback while visitors read it.'=>'第一次在博客评论我们介绍经验,内联反馈功能。这是一个互动的文章阅读选项和反馈的问题。现在文章作者为读者可以添加一些问题在某些文章内容的一部分,要求反馈而游客阅读它。','Once a question is added in article editor (backend), on article (front-end), readers will see a small comment icon next to the text part you\'ve selected. This feature engages post readers inviting them comment and leave a feedback without scrolling down and using the standard comment form. Thus they leave reply and react to post content or questions during the reading process.'=>'一旦问题被添加在文章编辑器(后端),在文章(前端),读者会看到旁边一个小评论图标你选中的文本部分。这个特性吸引读者后邀请他们评论,留下一个反馈没有向下滚动和使用标准的评论形式。因此他们离开回复和对文章内容或问题在阅读过程中。','The number of already left feedbacks will be displayed next to the feedback icon allowing people click and read other\'s feedbacks in the same place. Also, those feedbacks will be displayed with other standard comments in article comment section below.'=>'已留下的反馈数量将显示在反馈图标旁边，使人们可以在同一位置单击并阅读其他人的反馈。 同样，这些反馈将与其他标准评论一起显示在下面的文章评论部分。','Live Notification / Bubble'=>'实时通知/气泡',' In wpDiscuz 7 the real-time commenting becomes more live and attractive. It\'s based on REST API and doesn\'t overload your server. A specific sticky comment icon on your web pages, called &laquo;Bubble&raquo; keeps article readers and commenters up to date. It can display new comments as pop-up notification or as number in an orange circle.'=>' 在wpDiscuz 7中，实时评论变得更加生动有趣。 它基于REST API，不会使服务器过载。 网页上有一个特定的即时贴评论图标，称为“气泡”，可让文章阅读者和评论者保持最新状态。 它可以将新评论显示为弹出式通知，也可以显示为橙色圆圈中的数字。','Once new comment is posted, Bubble shows pop-up message with the new comment excerpt as it\'s shown on screenshot. The small &laquo;Reply&raquo; button allows to reply that comment immediately or readers can click on the pop-up notification and jump to that comment thread below the article. Just make sure the Bubble Live Update is enabled in wpDiscuz > Settings > Live Commenting and Notifications options.'=>'发布新评论后，Bubble会显示弹出消息，并带有新评论摘录，如屏幕截图所示。 小的“答复”按钮允许立即答复该评论，或者读者可以单击弹出通知并跳至文章下方的该评论线程。 只需确保在wpDiscuz>设置>实时评论和通知选项中启用了气泡实时更新。','If there is no new comments while visitor read the article, in most cases they don\'t even think about leaving some comment. The Bubble helps here too, it calls article readers to join to the discussion displaying them invite message. This message attracting readers attention and allows them fast and easy jump to comment area. Once page is loaded and visitor has read some content, it reminds about comments and calls to leave a reply.'=>'如果访客在阅读文章时没有新的评论，则在大多数情况下，他们甚至不考虑发表评论。 Bubble在这里也有帮助，它呼吁文章读者加入讨论并向他们显示邀请消息。 该消息吸引了读者的注意，并允许他们快速轻松地跳转到评论区域。 加载页面并访问者阅读了某些内容后，它会提醒您有关评论和呼叫的信息，以供回复。','wpDiscuz comment system design is totally changed. It comes with three nice layouts. You can even choose different layout for different pages. Three attractive, modern and clean layouts are ready to use. You can choose your proffered layout in wpDiscuz > Forms > Edit Comment Forms screen. Once the layout is changed, don\'t forget to delete all caches. Comment layouts are called simply &laquo;Layout #1&raquo;, &laquo;Layout #2&raquo;, &laquo;Layout #3&raquo;.'=>'wpDiscuz 注释系统设计完全改变了。它配备了三个漂亮的布局。您甚至可以选择不同的页面不同的布局。三个有吸引力的，现代和干净的布局是准备使用。您可以在 wpDiscuz 窗体>选择>的布局。更改布局后，不要忘记删除所有缓存。注释布局称为简单 [布局#1]，[布局#2]，[布局#3]。','Comment Layout #1'=>'评论版式＃1','Comment Layout #2'=>'注释布局#2','Comment Layout #3'=>'注释布局#3','The &laquo;Layout #1&raquo; is the simplest and cleanest layout. The &laquo;Layout #2&raquo; is designed for narrow comment sections. It displays comment content in wider area. The &laquo;Layout #3&raquo; layout is designed to accent comment thread hierarchy by colored vertical lines and indents.'=>'«布局＃1»是最简单，最干净的布局。 《布局2》是为狭窄的注释部分设计的。它在更大的区域显示评论内容。 «Layout＃3»布局旨在通过彩色垂直线和缩进来突出注释线程的层次结构。','Before, you had to create a Rating field in comment form to allow users rate article while they post a comment, there was no way to rate without commenting. Now you can allow users rate your articles without leavening a comment. wpDiscuz 7 has a built-in Post Rating system which is not based on comment form custom fields. You can see that on top of comment section like the left one on the screenshot below:'=>'之前,您必须创建一个评级在评论表单允许用户速率文章发布评论,没有评论,没有办法率。现在你可以允许用户速率没有发酵评论你的文章。wpDiscuz 7有一个内置的帖子评分系统不是基于评论表单定制字段。你可以看到在评论部分像左边下面的截图:','Overview & Comments Statistic'=>'概述和评论统计','All Comments'=>'所有评论','Comment Threads'=>'评论线程','Thread Replies'=>'线程中的回复','User Commenters'=>'用户评论者','Guest Commenters'=>'嘉宾评论员','Comment Statistic'=>'评论统计','All comments'=>'所有评论','Inline feedbacks'=>'在线反馈','Today'=>'今天','Last Week'=>'上周','Last Month'=>'上个月','Last 6 Months'=>'最近6个月','Last Year'=>'去年','All Time'=>'所有时间','Active Users and Guests'=>'活动用户和访客','Credits'=>'积分','Documentation'=>'文档','Getting Started'=>'入门指南','Manage Comment Forms'=>'管理评论表格','Manage Comment Layout'=>'管理评论布局','Plugin Customization'=>'插件定制','Translation'=>'翻译','Privacy and GDPR'=>'隐私和GDPR','Support & Community'=>'支持与社区','wpDiscuz Demo'=>'wpDiscuz演示版','wpDiscuz Support'=>'wpDiscuz支持','wpDiscuz Addons Support'=>'wpDiscuz插件支持','wpDiscuz Plugin Page'=>'wpDiscuz插件页面','Get all wpDiscuz premium addons with unlimited site license and save 90% with'=>'获得具有无限站点许可的所有wpDiscuz高级插件，并节省90％的费用','Contribute'=>'贡献','Help to Translate wpDiscuz'=>'帮助翻译wpDiscuz','We\'d really appreciate if you could help translating wpDiscuz to your language.'=>'如果您能帮助将wpDiscuz转换为您的语言，我们将非常感谢。','Just log in to the translation platform with your WordPress.org account, and suggest translations.'=>'只需使用您的WordPress.org帐户登录翻译平台，然后提出翻译建议。','Leave a Good Review'=>'留下一个好的评论','We love your reviews. This is the best way to say thank you to developers and support team.'=>'我们喜欢您的评论。 这是对开发人员和支持团队表示感谢的最佳方式。','wpDiscuz'=>'wpDiscuz','Support'=>'支持','Just 3 Steps to Complete Update!'=>'只需3个步骤即可完成更新！','Just 3 Steps to Complete Installation!'=>'仅需3个步骤即可完成安装！','Step 1'=>'第一步','Step 2'=>'第二步','Step 3'=>'第三步','Custom wpDiscuz template files are detected!'=>'自定义wpDiscuz模板文件被检测到！','Information: '=>'信息：','Your customized wpDiscuz template files are no longer compatible with wpDiscuz 7.  This is a doable major version update (from 5.x to 7.x) with totally redesigned comment system and template files. You can do the same customization on the new wpDiscuz 7 template files with the same upgrade-safe way in case the new comment layouts don\'t fit your needs. Please find those below.'=>'您自定义的wpDiscuz模板文件不再与wpDiscuz 7兼容。这是可行的主要版本更新（从5.x到7.x），具有完全重新设计的注释系统和模板文件。 如果新的注释布局不符合您的需求，您可以使用相同的升级安全方式对新的wpDiscuz 7模板文件进行相同的自定义。 请在下面找到这些。','Fix the problem: '=>'解决问题 ','Please remove wpDiscuz template files from your active theme\'s /wpdiscuz/ folder.'=>'请从活动主题的/ wpdiscuz /文件夹中删除wpDiscuz模板文件。','Use FTP client or hosting service cPanel > File Manager tool. WordPress theme folders are located in /wp-content/themes/ directory. The active theme folder can be detected by name.'=>'使用FTP客户端或托管服务cPanel>文件管理器工具。 WordPress主题文件夹位于/ wp-content / themes /目录中。 可以按名称检测活动主题文件夹。','Mark as solved'=>'标记为已解决','All wpDiscuz Addons are Deactivated!'=>'所有 wpDiscuz 加载项已停用！','All old versions of addons are not compatible with wpDiscuz 7, because of new comment layouts and template functions. In order to avoid errors wpDiscuz deactivates those during the update process.'=>'由于新的注释布局和模板功能，所有旧版本的插件都与 wpDiscuz 7 不兼容。为了避免错误wpDiscuz在更新过程中停用这些错误。','Please update wpDiscuz addons in Dashboard > Plugins admin page, then activate those back.'=>'请更新仪表板中 wpDiscuz >插件管理页面，然后重新激活这些插件。','Prior to the wpDiscuz 7 release, we\'ve released new versions of all wpDiscuz addons. If you\'ve already using the latest versions, just activate those back. If your license key is expired and you cannot update, please renew those addons at gVectors Store with 30% discount applied automatically at checkout page. Just make sure you\'re logged-in in the store with your customer account.'=>'Prior to the wpDiscuz 7 release, we’ve released new versions of all wpDiscuz addons. If you’ve already using the latest versions, just activate those back. If your license key is expired and you cannot update, please renew those addons at gVectors Store with 30% discount applied automatically at checkout page. Just make sure you’re logged-in in the store with your customer account.','Ok, I understood'=>'好吧， 我明白','Jetpack comments is active, please deactivate!'=>'Jetpack评论处于活动状态，请停用！','Jetpack Comments doesn\'t allow wpDiscuz comment form to be loaded on your posts and pages. It overwrites wpDiscuz Comment form.'=>'Jetpack 评论不允许将 wpDiscuz 评论表单加载到您的帖子和页面上。它覆盖 wpDiscuz 注释窗体。','Please disable Jetpack Comments.'=>'请禁用喷气背包评论。','Use the "Deactivate" button located next to the "Learn More" button. Just click on this button and Jetpack Comments will be deactivated. Once it\'s disabled, please delete all caches.'=>'使用"了解更多"按钮旁边的"停用"按钮。只需点击此按钮，Jetpack 评论将被停用。禁用后，请删除所有缓存。','I can\'t resolve the problems!'=>'我解决不了！','All problems displayed above have fixing tips in the same boxes. If, for some reason you can\'t solve those problems, we\'re ready to help you and fix those as soon as possible. Please open a support topic at gVectors support forum or contact as via support@gvectors.com email address. Our support team works from 6am till 6pm in GMT+0 timezone. Please be patient when you open a new support topic or when contacting us via email. We\'ll get back to you within 3-12 hours.'=>'上面显示的所有问题在相同的框中都有修复提示。如果由于某种原因您无法解决这些问题，我们将帮助您尽快解决这些问题。请在gVectors支持论坛上打开支持主题，或通过support@gvectors.com 电子邮件地址。我们的支持团队在GMT+0时区从早上6点工作到下午6点。当您打开新的支持主题或通过电子邮件与我们联系时，请耐心等待。我们会在3-12小时内回复你。','I want to downgrade to previous 5.x version!'=>'我想降级到以前的 5. x 版本！','To downgrade wpDiscuz, you should deactivate and delete wpDiscuz 7 plugin. Then download the previous 5.3.2 version ZIP file from wpDiscuz plugin page (use dropdown menu under statistic graphics). And install the ZIP file in Dashboard > Plugins > Add Plugin admin page. The downgrading is only recommended to gain a time to do template customizations or wait for help from our support team. Once the issues are resolved, you should update to latest wpDiscuz version.'=>'要降级 wpDiscuz， 您应该停用并删除 wpDiscuz 7 插件。然后从 wpDiscuz 插件页面下载以前的 5.3.2 版本 ZIP 文件（使用统计图形下的下拉菜单）。并在仪表板和插件中安装 ZIP >，>插件管理页面。降级仅建议获得执行模板自定义或等待支持团队的帮助的时间。问题解决后，应更新到最新的 wpDiscuz 版本。','Comments Style & Layout'=>'注释样式和布局','Comments Style'=>'评论样式','Light'=>'浅色','Dark'=>'深色','Choose Your Comments Layout'=>'选择注释布局','Layout #1'=>'布局1','Layout #2'=>'布局2','Layout #3'=>'布局3','Comments Layout #1'=>'注释布局#1','Comments Layout #2'=>'评论版式＃2','Comments Layout #3'=>'注释布局#3','Comment Bubble is a sticky comment icon on your web pages. It keeps article readers and commenters up to date. It displays new comments as pop-up information or as a number in an orange circle.'=>'评论气泡是网页上的粘性注释图标。它使文章读者和评论者保持最新。它将新注释显示为弹出信息或橙色圆圈中的数字。','The Bubble is also designed to invite article readers to comment. It displays invite message allowing them fast and easy jump to comment area.'=>'此气泡还旨在邀请文章读者发表评论。它显示邀请消息，允许他们快速轻松地跳转到评论区域。','Disable'=>'禁用','Bubble Live Update'=>'气泡实时更新','Content Left'=>'左侧内容','Left Corner'=>'左角落','Right Corner'=>'右角','More News'=>'更多新闻','Increase Your Comments!'=>'增加您的评论！','Add Inline Commenting forms in article!'=>'在文章中添加相关评论表单！','Ask questions to readers and discuss directly on article content!'=>'向读者提问，直接讨论文章内容！','Great News! Now you can add questions for readers on certain part of article content and ask for feedback while visitors read it.'=>'好消息！现在，您可以向读者添加文章内容某些部分的问题，并在访问者阅读时征求反馈。','Select a part of text, add inline commenting form in post content using the green &laquo;Comment&raquo; button on post editor toolbar. Once it\'s added in article editor (backend), on article (front-end) readers will see a small comment icon next to the text part you\'ve selected.'=>'选择一部分文字，使用帖子编辑器工具栏上的绿色“评论”按钮在帖子内容中添加内嵌评论表单。将其添加到文章编辑器（后端）后，在文章（前端）上，读者会在您选择的文本部分旁边看到一个小注释图标。','Article Rating vs Comment Rating'=>'评级和评论文章评级','Enable Article Rating'=>'使文章评级','Before, you had to create a Rating field in comment form to allow users rate article while they post a comment, there was no way to rate without commenting. Now you can allow users rate your articles without leaving a comment. wpDiscuz 7 has a built-in Article Rating system which is not based on comment form custom fields and appears on top of comment section, under the article content.'=>'之前,您必须创建一个评级在评论表单允许用户速率文章发布评论,没有评论,没有办法率。现在你可以允许用户速率没有留下一个评论你的文章。wpDiscuz 7有一个内置的评级系统不是基于条评论表单自定义字段和出现在评论部分,根据文章内容。','Finish Update'=>'完成更新','Finish Installation'=>'完成安装','Next Step &raquo;'=>'下一步 |','Thank You!'=>'谢谢！','Start Using wpDiscuz'=>'开始使用 wpDiscuz','Find an option...'=>'找到一个选项...','Open Settings'=>'打开设置','Addons Settings'=>'附加组件设置','Back'=>'返回','Reset Tab Options'=>'重置选项','Reset All Options'=>'重置所有选项','Save Changes'=>'保存更改','wpDiscuz Front-end Phrases'=>'WpDiscuz前端短语','General'=>'通用','Date/Time'=>'日期 / 时间','Notification'=>'提醒','Follow'=>'关注','Social Login'=>'社交登陆','User Settings'=>'用户设置','Errors'=>'错误','Media'=>'媒体','Reset Phrases'=>'重置短语','wpDiscuz Tools'=>'wpDiscuz工具','Here you can manage comment content related options, such as comment text length, comment content breaking, comment image attachment... By default wpDiscuz allows to attach one image with comment. For an advanced media uploading and file attachment options we recommend %s addon.'=>'在这里，您可以管理评论内容相关的选项，如评论文本长度、评论内容中断、评论图像附件。。。默认情况下，wpDiscuz 允许在注释中附加一个图像。对于高级媒体上传和文件附件选项，我们建议%s个插件。','Min'=>'最小','Max'=>'最大','File Attachment Settings'=>'文件附件设置','Select All'=>'全选','Unselect All'=>'取消全选','Invert Selection'=>'反选','Server \'upload_max_filesize\' is '=>'服务器"upload_max_filesize"是','Server \'post_max_size\' is '=>'服务器“post_max_size”是','Width (px)'=>'宽度 (px)','Height (px)'=>'高度（px）','wpDiscuz allows you to customize comment form layout and fields. You can create as much comment forms as you want and attach those to certain post type or page. Please navigate to %s page to manage comment form specific settings.'=>'wpDiscuz 允许您自定义注释窗体布局和字段。您可以创建尽可能多的注释表单，并将其附加到某些帖子类型或页面。请导航到%s以管理注释表单的特定设置。','Comment Form Manager'=>'评论表格管理器','collapsed'=>'已折叠','expanded'=>'已扩张','Mobile and Desktop'=>'移动端和台式机','Only Desktop'=>'仅PC端','None'=>'无','Disable formatting toolbar'=>'禁用格式工具栏','Enable formatting toolbar'=>'启用格式工具栏','Go to "Comment Content and Media" admin page to manage image attachment settings'=>'转到“评论内容和媒体”管理页面以管理图像附件设置','Replace non-https content to simple link URLs'=>'将非https内容替换为简单链接网址','Just replace http protocols to https (https may not be supported by content provider)'=>'只需将http协议替换为https（内容提供商可能不支持https）','Ignore non-https content'=>'忽略非https内容','Do not redirect'=>'不重定向','Current Wordpress date/time format'=>'WordPress当前日期/时间格式','Thank you!'=>'谢谢！','Comment and User Cache'=>'评论和用户缓存','Maintenance'=>'维护','Remove vote data'=>'移除投票数据','Purge comments and users caches'=>'清除评论和用户缓存','Article Inline Feedback feature is an interactive article reading option with author\'s questions and readers feedback (comments). Now article authors can add some questions for readers on certain part of article content and ask for feedback while visitors read it.'=>'文章在线反馈功能是一种交互式的文章阅读选项，其中包含作者的问题和读者的反馈（评论）。 现在，文章作者可以在文章内容的某些部分为读者添加一些问题，并在访问者阅读文章时征求反馈。','You can add Inline Feedback button in post content using &laquo;Comment&raquo; button on post editor toolbar.'=>'您可以使用帖子编辑器工具栏上的 [注释] 按钮在帖子内容中添加内联反馈按钮。','Once a question is added in article editor (backend), on article (front-end) readers will see a small comment icon next to the text part you\'ve selected. This feature engages post readers inviting them comment and leave a feedback while reading without scrolling down and using the standard comment form.'=>'在文章编辑器（后端）中添加问题后，读者在文章（前端）上将看到所选文本部分旁边的小注释图标。此功能吸引帖子读者邀请他们发表评论，并在阅读时留下反馈，无需向下滚动并使用标准评论表单。','Animate (blink and wiggle)'=>'动画 （闪烁和摆动）','Open the Feedback Form on scroll'=>'在滚动时打开反馈表','User Labels are small rectangles with specific background colors indicating comment author role, such as Guest, Member, Author, Admin, etc... These labels can be enabled and disabled for certain user role. Also you can change label colors using according options below.<br> Besides labels you can enable User Reputation, Badges and Ranks based on user activity, using %s addon. This addon integrates wpDiscuz comment system with an adaptive user points management plugin %s.'=>'用户标签是具有特定背景颜色的小矩形，指示注释作者角色，如来宾、成员、作者、管理员等。可以为某些用户角色启用和禁用这些标签。此外，您也可以根据以下选项更改标签颜色。<br> 除了标签，您可以使用附加组件启用用户信誉、徽章和基于用户 %s 活动的排名。此附加组件将wpDiscuz注释系统与自适应用户点管理插件集成在一起 %s 。','label color'=>'标签色','Example: #00FF00'=>'例如：#00FF00','In wpDiscuz 7 the real-time commenting becomes more live and attractive. It\'s based on REST API and doesn\'t overload your server. A specific sticky comment icon on your web pages, called &laquo;Bubble&raquo; keeps article readers and commenters up to date. It displays new comments as pop-up information or as a number in an orange circle.'=>'在 wpDiscuz 7 中，实时评论变得更加真实和有吸引力。它基于 REST API，不会使服务器过载。网页中特定的粘性评论图标称为 "泡泡"，使文章读者和评论者保持最新状态。它将新注释显示为弹出信息或橙色圆圈中的数字。','This Bubble is also designed to invite article readers to comment. It displays invite message allowing them fast and easy jump to comment area.'=>'此气泡还旨在邀请文章读者发表评论。它显示邀请消息，允许他们快速轻松地跳转到评论区域。','You can enabled comments live update without the Bubble too. There is a separate live update option to keep comment list real-time updating.'=>'您也可以启用实时评论更新，而无需冒泡。有一个单独的实时更新选项，可以使评论列表实时更新。','Seconds'=>'秒','Minute'=>'分钟','Minutes'=>'分钟','Here you can manage commenters authorization and data control related settings. wpDiscuz is focused on user engagement and community building ideas, therefore it\'s integrated with community builder plugins like wpForo Forum, BuddyPress, etc... With these plugins comment authors are linked to their profile pages. In case you want to display commenters profile and activity information directly on comment list, please be sure to check out the %s addon.'=>'在这里，您可以管理注释者授权和数据控制相关设置。wpDiscuz 专注于用户参与和社区建设理念， 因此它与社区构建者插件集成， 如 wpForo 论坛， BuddyPress 等...有了这些插件，评论作者被链接到他们的个人资料页面。如果您要直接在评论列表中显示评论者配置文件和活动信息，请务必在添加%s。','Enable button'=>'启用按钮','Show Activity Tab'=>'显示活动标签','Show Subscriptions Tab'=>'显示订阅选项卡','Show Follows Tab'=>'显示跟随标签','WordPress has already all necessary tools to moderate commends. You can approve, unapprove, mark as spam, delete and do other things with comments in WordPress Dashboard > Comments admin page. <br><br>On front-end you can only edit, close and stick comments. In case you want to have all moderation options on front-end, we recommend checkout %s addon. Besides the comment editing, closing and sticking options, here you can limit users commenting activity. You can set max number of comments per user per post or sitewide, allow them only comment or only reply.'=>'WordPress 已经拥有了一切必要的工具来缓和赞扬。您可以批准，未经批准，标记为垃圾邮件，删除和做其他事情与WordPress仪表板&gt;评论管理页面的评论。 <br><br>在前端，您只能编辑、关闭和粘注注释。如果您想在前端拥有所有节制选项，我们建议 %s 结账插件。除了评论编辑，关闭和坚持选项，在这里你可以限制用户的评论活动。您可以设置每个用户每个帖子或站点的最大评论次数，只允许他们发表评论或只回复。','Do not allow'=>'不允许','Hour'=>'小时','Hours'=>'小时','Unlimit'=>'无限','Per Post'=>'每个文章的最大%s次数','Sitewide'=>'全部网站','Both'=>'两者','Max number of comments'=>'评论数','You have two ways to add Post Rating for your blog posts and articles. The first, comment independent type is enabled by default and appears on top of comment section. It allows people rate your articles without leaving comments. '=>'有两种方法可以为您的博客文章和文章添加帖子评级。第一个注释独立类型默认启用，显示在注释部分的顶部。它允许人们评价你的文章，而不留下评论。','The second type, is the old, comment depended way. You should create a "Rating" custom field in comment form allowing people to rate while they leave a comment. If you\'ve already configured the second type (Rating comment field) in comment form, the first type will be automatically disabled. Both types of ratings can be managed in %s'=>'第二种类型，是老的，评论靠的方式。您应该在注释窗体中创建"评级"自定义字段，允许人们在发表评论时进行评级。如果在注释窗体中配置了第二种类型（评级注释字段），则将自动禁用第一个类型。两种类型的评级都可以在%s','Comment Form Manager &raquo;'=>'评论表管理器','Before Comment Form'=>'注释表单前','Before Content'=>'内容之前','After Content'=>'内容之后','Display ratings on non-singular pages'=>'在任何单一页面上显示评级','Rating Stars Hover Color'=>'评级星星悬停颜色','Rating Stars Inactive Color'=>'评级星星非活动颜色','Rating Stars Active Color'=>'评级星级活跃颜色','Please %s with Google to obtain the Site Key and Secret Key for %s. Then insert those keys in according fields below.'=>'请%s谷歌获取网站密钥和密钥，以便%s。然后根据下面的字段在中插入这些键。','register your domain'=>'注册您的域','reCAPTCHA Version 2'=>'reCAPTCHA 版本2','If you want to use the latest Version 3 - Invisible Google reCAPTCHA with comment form, please checkout %s addon. This will make your commenters life easier, letting them pass through with ease.'=>'如果您想使用最新的版本3-带注释表单的Invisible Google reCAPTCHA，请签出%s插件。这将使您的评论者的生活更轻松，使他们轻松通过。','Auto'=>'自动','SocketPost'=>'套接字','CurlPost'=>'卷曲柱','Post'=>'文章','reCAPTCHA v2'=>'reCAPTCHA v2','reCAPTCHA V2 Site Key'=>'reCAPTCHA V2 站点密钥','reCAPTCHA V2 Secret Key'=>'CAPTCHA v2 密钥','Example en'=>'例如：en','Language codes'=>'语言代码','To start using Facebook Login and Share Buttons you should get Facebook Application Key and Secret for your website. Please follow to this'=>'要开始使用Facebook登录和共享按钮，您应该获得您的网站的Facebook应用程序密钥和秘密。 请按照这个','instruction &raquo;'=>'說明操作 &raquo;','Valid OAuth Redirect URI'=>'有效的OAuth重定向URI','Application ID'=>'应用程序ID','Application Secret'=>'应用秘钥','Consumer Key (API Key)'=>'Consumer Key (API Key)','Consumer Secret (API Secret)'=>'Consumer Secret (API Secret)','To start using Google Login Button you should get Client ID and  Client Secret for your website. Please follow to this'=>'要开始使用谷歌登录按钮，你应该得到您的客户ID和客户机密为您的网站。请关注此','Permitted URI redirects'=>'允许的 URI 重定向','Client ID'=>'客户端ID','Client Secret'=>'客户端密钥','Origin URL'=>'原生网址','API Token'=>'API令牌','To start using Disqus Login Button you should get Public Key and Secret Key. Please follow to this '=>'要开始使用 Disqus 登录按钮，您应该获取公钥和密钥。请关注此','Redirect URI'=>'重定向URI','Public Key'=>'公钥','Secure Key'=>'安全密钥','To start using Wordpress.com Login Button you should get Client ID and Client Secret. Please follow to this '=>'若要开始使用Wordpress.com登录按钮，应获取客户端 ID 和客户端密钥。请关注此','To start using Instagram Login Button you should get Client ID and Client Secret. Please follow to this '=>'若要开始使用LinkedIn登录按钮，应获取客户端 ID 和客户端密钥。请关注此','App Secret'=>'App 密钥','To start using Linkedin Login Button you should get Client ID and Client Secret. Please follow to this '=>'若要开始使用LinkedIn登录按钮，应获取客户端 ID 和客户端密钥。请关注此','To start using Yandex Login Button you should get Client ID and Client Secret. Please follow to this '=>'若要开始使用LinkedIn登录按钮，应获取客户端 ID 和客户端密钥。请关注此','ID'=>'ID','Password'=>'密码','To start using WeChat Login Button you should get AppID and Secret. Please follow to this '=>'要开始使用微信登录按钮，您应该获得应用和秘密。请遵循这一点','Secret'=>'密钥','To start using Weibo Login Button you should get App Key and App Secret. Please follow to this '=>'要开始使用微博登录按钮，您应该获取应用密钥和应用程序机密。请关注此','Key'=>'键','To start using Tencent QQ Login Button you should get AppID and AppKey. Please follow to this '=>'要开始使用腾讯QQ登录按钮，你应该得到 AppID 和 AppKey 。请关注此','To start using Baidu Login Button you should get Client Id and Client Secret. Please follow to this '=>'若要开始使用LinkedIn登录按钮，应获取客户端 ID 和客户端密钥。请关注此','wpDiscuz allows users to get all kind of news from your website comment system, such as new comments, new replies, double opt-in subscription, user mentioning, user following and new comments by followed users. You can manage all those options here. All those options are based on email notifications. You can manage email templates in wpDiscuz > Phrases > Email Tab. <br>In wpDiscuz > Dashboard page, you can find a quick overview of user subscriptions. For an advanced subscriptions management tool, please checkout %s addon.'=>'wpDiscuz 允许用户从您的网站评论系统获取各种新闻，例如新评论、新回复、双重选择加入订阅、用户提及、用户关注以及以下用户的新评论。您可以在这里管理所有这些选项。所有这些选项都基于电子邮件通知。您可以在 wpDiscuz 和短语>中管理>模板。 <br>在 wpDiscuz >仪表板页面中，您可以快速查看用户订阅。对于高级订阅管理工具，请查看 %s 加载项。','Subscribe to all comments of this post'=>'订阅此帖子的所有评论','Subscribe to all replies to my comments'=>'订阅所有回复我的评论','Available shortcodes'=>'可用的短代码','Approved'=>'批准','Here you can find all necessary options to control comment threads loading, displaying and sorting functions. Using "Comment List Loading Type", "Comments Pagination Type" and "Display only parent comments" options, you can get the highest page loading speed.  Also you can manage comment thread filtering buttons.'=>'在这里，您可以找到所有必要的选项来控制注释线程的加载，显示和排序功能。 使用“评论列表加载类型”，“评论分页类型”和“仅显示父评论”选项，可以获得最快的页面加载速度。 您还可以管理注释线程过滤按钮。','Load with page'=>'使用页面加载','Initiates AJAX loading once page loading is complete'=>'页面加载完成后启动 AJAX 加载','Initiate AJAX loading after page'=>'在页面后启动 AJAX 加载','Display [View Comments] button to load comments manually'=>'显示 [查看注释] 按钮以手动加载注释','Display [View Comments] button'=>'显示 [查看注释] 按钮','[Load more] Button'=>'[加载更多] 按钮','[Load rest of all comments] Button'=>'[加载剩余评论] 按钮','Load all comments'=>'加载所有评论','Lazy load comments on scrolling'=>'滚动式延迟加载评论','Here you can manage comment layout components. You can display/hide certain button or information on comment threads, as well as commenters\' avatars and comment voting options.'=>'您可以在此处管理评论布局组件。 您可以显示/隐藏评论线程上的某些按钮或信息，以及评论者的头像和评论投票选项。','wpDiscuz 7 comes with three modern and totally different comment thread layouts. They are called Layout #1, Layout #2 and Layout #3.'=>'wpDiscuz 7 附带三个现代和完全不同的注释线程布局。它们称为"布局#1布局、#2布局和布局#3。','Comment Thread Layout #1'=>'注释线程布局#1','Comment Thread Layout #2'=>'注释线程布局#2','Comment Thread Layout #3'=>'注释线程布局#3','You can select different comment thread layout for different comment forms in %s'=>'您可以在其中为不同的注释窗体选择不同的注释%s','Avatar Settings'=>'头像设置','Comment Voting Buttons'=>'评论投票按钮','total count'=>'合计数','separate count'=>'区分计数','Layout Components'=>'布局组件','Here you can manage comment thread styles, custom colors and add custom CSS. By default wpDiscuz comes with &laquo;Light&raquo; style. If your theme style is dark, we recommend choose the &laquo;Dark&raquo; option for comments too. In case you want to totally customize comment style or create it from scrat